1
00:00:13,599 --> 00:00:14,279
Li Qiankun.

2
00:00:15,359 --> 00:00:17,600
Didn't Master Zhang beg you the same way back then?

3
00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:19,920
Did you spare him?

4
00:00:20,359 --> 00:00:20,640
You...

5
00:00:21,839 --> 00:00:22,600
You're setting me up!

6
00:00:23,079 --> 00:00:24,399
I'll... I'll beat you to death!

7
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:32,920
Li Qiankun.

8
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,320
If you had done less evil,

9
00:00:36,039 --> 00:00:37,200
spared Master Zhang,

10
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,600
spared those herb farmers in Lijia Village,

11
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,759
maybe I could've spared you too.

12
00:00:42,759 --> 00:00:44,280
Everything happening now

13
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,000
is what you brought upon yourself.

14
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,439
What the hell do you want?

15
00:00:53,039 --> 00:00:54,200
I don't want anything.

16
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:57,719
I just want to ask you a few questions.

17
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,119
What questions?

18
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:03,079
The Wang Family making drugs from that formula,

19
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,359
what exactly are they trying to do?

20
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:07,680
What formula?

21
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,439
What drugs?

22
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,439
I don't know what you're talking about.

23
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:16,599
The Wang Family got a formula from us years ago,

24
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:20,400
one that treats critical and terminal illnesses,

25
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:22,480
capable of raising the dead.

26
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:26,079
If they develop that drug,

27
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:28,400
forget just Beishi,

28
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:32,079
they'd have no rival in the entire national pharma market.

29
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,760
But the herb dosages haven't been calibrated yet.

30
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,959
Plus, the ingredients

31
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:43,079
include Aconite, Pinellia Rhizome, and others.

32
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:46,400
So the Wang Family had you grow those in Lijia Village?

33
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,400
Is what you're saying true?

34
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,159
Absolutely true.

35
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,959
My parents died because of this.

36
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,039
They deceived me.

37
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,759
They deceived me!

38
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,199
They said it was for growing banned drugs

39
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,520
to ship overseas to develop foreign markets.

40
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:21,960
I checked. The Wang Family has a mole in the hospital.

41
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,280
Just like you said,

42
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,159
it's connected to the formula.

43
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,800
And also...

44
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,240
I have to tell you about someone.

45
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,639
Feifan.

46
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,360
Senior Brother.

47
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,599
Are you close with Dr. Li Xiande?

48
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:49,280
Who?

49
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:50,439
Li Xiande.

50
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,879
The one in the ER.

51
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:57,960
He doesn't talk much, quite introverted.

52
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,000
I'm not close with him.

53
00:02:59,159 --> 00:02:59,639
Why?

54
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,360
Why are you suddenly asking about him?

55
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,960
I've noticed he's been acting strange lately.

56
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,159
This guy, at the hospital,

57
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,280
barely has any presence.

58
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,240
What makes you think something's off?

59
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,439
I noticed the ER patients he treats

60
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:41,520
have a higher mortality rate than those of other doctors.

61
00:03:43,919 --> 00:03:45,520
Isn't that just poor medical skills?

62
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,680
What's strange about that?

63
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,439
Hurry, get him to the resus room!

64
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,039
Hold on.

65
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:59,039
The patient's left hand is clutching his right chest.

66
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,520
It hurts, it hurts.

67
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,319
It hurts.

68
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,280
It hurts, it hurts.

69
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,680
The tenderness is on the chest wall, not the precordium.

70
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,400
The pain is stabbing, not crushing.

71
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,280
The patient has a history of shingles, right?

72
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:18,240
Yes, diagnosed last month.

73
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:24,279
The ECG shows no ST-segment changes.

74
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,000
External pathogen invasion on the back

75
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:27,480
has caused intercostal neuralgia.

76
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,879
This isn't a heart attack.

77
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,560
Remember this.

78
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,040
Before putting a patient under the knife,

79
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:36,000
first figure out which hand is clutching the chest.

80
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:42,480
President Wang.

81
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:45,000
Ren Feifan seems to suspect me already.

82
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,000
I can't stay at the hospital any longer.

83
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:48,360
Otherwise...

84
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,879
What are you panicking about?

85
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:52,319
Everything requires evidence.

86
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,319
Without proof, what can Ren Feifan do to you?

87
00:04:55,959 --> 00:04:57,160
But... but he...

88
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,399
But what?

89
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,079
Hurry back and do your job properly.

90
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,879
I'll handle Ren Feifan.

91
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,040
Okay.

92
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,079
Dad.

93
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,560
Li Xiande is still too green.

94
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,199
He can't weather a storm.

95
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:21,920
Better to cut him loose.

96
00:05:23,519 --> 00:05:24,000
Right.

97
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,000
I'll go take care of it now.

98
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,279
Since you can't protect me,

99
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,600
don't blame me for not risking my life for you.

100
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:51,639
Senior Brother.

101
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:53,759
Double-check the middle section again.

102
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:02,759
What are you looking at?

103
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,519
Let's hurry up and go.

104
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,439
The patient is critical.

105
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,959
Hello, Feifan, where are you?

106
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:18,000
Wang Wenhao and his son want to silence Li Xiande now.

107
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:21,199
I bet he has the evidence you want.

108
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:24,000
Li Xiande's out of options and wants to meet me.

109
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,399
I have to take this risk.

110
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,720
Then why didn't he go to you directly?

111
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:29,279
Because he wants to both save his own life and get away cleanly.

112
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:29,759
So...

113
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,399
where's he meeting you?

114
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:33,319
I'll send you the location right away.

115
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,720
Just get to me as soon as you can.

116
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,759
Senior Brother, go see the patient first.

117
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,480
I'll go after Li Xiande.

118
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:41,759
All right.

119
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:10,920
Li Xiande.

120
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,000
Li Xiande.

121
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:23,759
Li Xiande.

122
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,920
Li Xiande, come out.

123
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,800
You've got guts.

124
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,639
Coming alone?

125
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,639
Do you know why I called you here?

126
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,360
The Wang father and son want to silence you.

127
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,279
And you want a way out.

128
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:46,319
I have a little secret about Wang Wenhao.

129
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,879
I can hand it over to Ren Feifan.

130
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:51,319
But I need to secure my own safety first.

131
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,720
I can have Ren Feifan come here now.

132
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,000
You can tell him face to face.

133
00:07:58,439 --> 00:08:00,560
Even he can't guarantee my safety.

134
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:03,519
So what exactly do you want?

135
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,879
I think you're just bluffing.

136
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:09,199
You have no evidence of the Wang Family's crimes at all.

137
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:10,680
I definitely have the evidence.

138
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:12,360
But after thinking it over,

139
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:15,279
I'm safer with you as the middleman.

140
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:27,839
Hello, Ruojin.

141
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,120
I'm here.

142
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,560
Where are you?

143
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,679
Just as I thought.

144
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,519
It turns out the person Xu Ruojin trusts most is you.

145
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:40,120
No wonder she'd risk everything to do something for you.

146
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,759
Let me tell you.

147
00:08:42,279 --> 00:08:44,320
Xu Ruojin is in my hands right now.

148
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,399
I know that to both you and Wang Wenhao,

149
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,360
she is the most important person.

150
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:49,679
Of course,

151
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,399
Director Ren,

152
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,759
you're far more honorable than Wang Wenhao.

153
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,519
How about we make a deal.

154
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,120
I'll take Xu Ruojin with me first,

155
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:02,840
as a Get-out-of-jail-free card.

156
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:04,720
Once I've escaped safely,

157
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,399
I'll return her and the evidence to you.

158
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:08,679
Ruojin!

159
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:09,440
Ruojin!

160
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,240
Li Xian—

161
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,039
Ruojin!

162
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:19,919
Ruojin!

163
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,080
Ruojin!

164
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,279
Ruojin!

165
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,480
Ruojin!

166
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:38,759
Ruojin!

167
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,240
Ren Feifan.

168
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:17,440
Nothing good ever happens to my daughter when you're involved.

169
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:18,840
Why are you here?

170
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,879
Look what you've done to her!

171
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,879
She's already engaged.

172
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:23,320
There's nothing between you two anymore.

173
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,600
Why wasn't it you who got hurt?

174
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:27,360
You Jinx!

175
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:31,320
Years ago, you got your parents killed.

176
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:33,679
Now you want to get Ruojin killed too?

177
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,320
Get out!

178
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,720
Get the hell out!

179
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,960
Get out, I said!

180
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,559
Out!

181
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,000
During Ren Feifan's tenure,

182
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,600
a major incident occurred at this hospital.

183
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:53,720
The board has decided to remove Ren Feifan as Director.

184
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,320
Ruojin is severely injured.

185
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,440
Li Xiande is dead.

186
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:19,759
Why?

187
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:22,120
Every time, I'm just a step away.

188
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:25,120
Whenever I get close to the evidence,

189
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,000
it always slips through my fingers.

190
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,279
Feifan, Feifan!

191
00:11:44,399 --> 00:11:45,080
Calm down.

192
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,879
This whole thing is a setup.

193
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,000
It's not, Feifan.

194
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,399
I raped her.

195
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:55,440
I'll come with you.
